/Sequana\"}, {\"begin\": 3699, \"end\": 3704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.750208544786228e-13, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3624}, {\"ngram\": \"the goddess\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3665}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea was to have a Pagan festival linked to the Gods of Olympus.\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3729, \"end\": 3734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\", \"score\": 0.9999999998426574, \"rank\": 1.5763611957785132e-10, \"text\": \"Pagan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3714}, {\"ngram\": \"the Gods\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3762}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympus\", \"from\": 3766, \"to\": 3773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will never find in me a desire to mock and denigrate anyone.\\\"\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a desire\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3809}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some were supportive of the artistic vision, arguing the tableau was fighting to make a statement on inclusivity.\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 3955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the artistic vision\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3885}, {\"ngram\": \"the tableau\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3906}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 3939}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusivity\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 3954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know in the LGBTQ community in France we are far from what the ceremony showed.\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 4040, \"