ngram\": \"trial\", \"from\": 4188, \"to\": 4193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to French newspaper Le Parisien, Katerine said in French that the entire ceremony was \\\"moving\\\" and \\\"grandiose.\\\"\", \"from\": 4260, \"to\": 4380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4272, \"end\": 4278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9984447060073379, \"rank\": 0.0013906733785231324, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4289, \"end\": 4300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Parisien\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\"}, {\"begin\": 4319, \"end\": 4325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9984447060073379, \"rank\": 0.0013906733785231324, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Katerine\", \"from\": 4302, \"to\": 4310}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire ceremony\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was proud of it because it's my culture.\", \"from\": 4382, \"to\": 4425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my culture\", \"from\": 4414, \"to\": 4424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are full of different people and each person lives in their own way and above all has the right to do so.\", \"from\": 4426, \"to\": 4534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different people\", \"from\": 4441, \"to\": 4457}, {\"ngram\": \"each person\", \"from\": 4462, \"to\": 4473}, {\"ngram\": \"their own way\", \"from\": 4483, \"to\": 4496}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 4515, \"to