season\", \"from\": 5282, \"to\": 5298}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Drag Race France\", \"from\": 5302, \"to\": 5319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought it would be a five-minute drag event with queer representation.\", \"from\": 5361, \"to\": 5435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a five-minute drag event\", \"from\": 5384, \"to\": 5408}, {\"ngram\": \"queer representation\", \"from\": 5414, \"to\": 5434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was amazed.\", \"from\": 5436, \"to\": 5449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It started with Lady Gaga, then we had drag queens, a huge rave, and a fire in the sky.\", \"from\": 5450, \"to\": 5537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5466, \"end\": 5475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 5489, \"to\": 5500}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge rave\", \"from\": 5502, \"to\": 5513}, {\"ngram\": \"a fire\", \"from\": 5519, \"to\": 5525}, {\"ngram\": \"the sky\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It felt like a crowning all over again.\", \"from\": 5538, \"to\": 5577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a crowning\", \"from\": 5551, \"to\": 5561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am proud to see my friends and queer people on the world stage,\\\" Le Filip said.\", \"from\": 5578, \"to\": 5659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my friends\", \"from\": 5596, \"to\": 5606}, {\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 5611, \"to\": 5623}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 5627, \"to\": 5642}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Filip\", \"from\": 5645, \"to\": 5653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others, including celebrities, U.S. political figures and Catholic church leaders, expressed outrage at the scene.\", \"from\": 5661, \"to